extends ./templates/template.pug
block title&description
  meta(name="description" content="Title Tag: Dallas SEO Company, Web Design and Development, Internet Marketing\n" +
  "Meta Description: Assure Studios is a full service digital marketing company based out of Dallas Texas. We specialize in Search Engine Optimization (SEO), web design and development, social media management, website maintenance and more. Contact us today for a free consultation!")
  title Assure Studios | SEO, Web Design, and Digital Marketing
block bodyTag
  -var bodyTag="home"
  body(id=`${bodyTag}`)

block banner
  .banner.container-fluid
    .row.align-items-center.justify-content-center.flex-wrap-reverse
      .col-xxl-12
        .banner-title Assure Studios
        h1 We provide simple marketing strategies that work,
          | <wbr>
          |  so you can focus on what you do best - running your business. </wbr>





block content
 .section.intro.container-fluid
     .row.align-items-center.flex-wrap-reverse
       .col-xl-12
         h2 We Are Assure Studios
         p Assure Studios is digital marketing and web development company based out of Dallas, Texas. Our Mission is to help small businesses and churches grow and prosper through Digital Marketing Strategies.
         P We offer Search Engine Optimization (SEO), social media management, social media marketing, and web development.
         p We create plans developed around simple-to-understand and measurable smart goals. We work with you to help build your brand and your business.
         p.mb-4 If you are a church here's  &nbsp;
          wbr
          a(href="./churches.html" title ="church services") Our church marketing services.
       .col-xl-12
         picture
           source(media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-welcome@0.1x.png")
           source(media="(max-width: 799px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-welcome@0.25x.png")
           source(media="(min-width: 800px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-welcome@0.3x.png")
           img( width="1200" height="1200" src="./img/assure-studios-welcome@0.3x.png" alt="assure studios picture of papers and computers")
 .section
     .container-fluid
       .row.align-items-center
         .col-lg-12
           picture
             source(media="(max-width: 400px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-need-digital-marketing@0.1x.png")
             source(media="(max-width: 799px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-need-digital-marketing@0.15x.png")
             source(media="(min-width: 800px)" srcset="./img/assure-studios-need-digital-marketing@0.2x.png")
             img(width="1200" height="1200" src="./img/assure-studios-need-digital-marketing@0.3x.png" alt="assure studios picture of papers and computers")

         .col-lg-12
           h2 Why you need digital Marketing
           p.mb-5 Digital marketing is essential for businesses of all sizes. By helping businesses find new customers and cultivate relationships with their established and potential customers, digital marketing can help businesses grow. Additionally, digital marketing can help businesses increase brand recognition and revenue.
           h3 Where to get started
           p To get started with digital marketing, businesses can take advantage of Assure Studios free SEO audits and free SEO consultations. These services will help businesses identify areas where they need to improve their online presence and develop a plan to improve their digital marketing strategy.
 .section.content-section
  include ../pug/partials/free-stuff-partial
 .section.container-fluid.services
  .row.justify-content-between
    .col-12
      h2 Our Professional Services
      h3.sectionHelper Our digital marketing services revolves around easy-to-follow smart goals.
    .card.col-xl-6.col-lg-12
      .card-icon
      h3 Digital Marketing
      p Digital marketing is the use of the internet to display advertising, and the use of social media channels to reach, connect and engage with customers.
      button(onClick="location.href='./digital-marketing.html'").button.assure-button Learn About Our<br> Digital Marketing Services
    .card.col-xl-6.col-lg-12
      .card-icon
      h3 SEO
      p Search Engine Optimization or SEO is the activity of assuring a website can easily be found in search engines; when people are looking for products or services your business offers
      button(onClick="location.href='./seo.html'").button.assure-button Learn About Our<br> SEO Services
    .card.col-xl-6.col-lg-12
      .card-icon
      h3 Website Development
      p Website development is about creating well crafted websites that are mobile friendly, accessible and secure.
      button(onClick="location.href='./web-development.html'").button.assure-button Learn About Our<br> Web Dev Services
    .card.col-xl-6.col-lg-12
      .card-icon
      h3 Consulting
      p Let us design a digital marketing strategy that outlines how your business will achieve its marketing goals
      button(onClick="location.href='./consulting.html'").button.assure-button Learn About Our<br> Consulting Services


 .section.container-fluid
   h2 The Faqs
   p Top three questions about digital marketing.
   .row.justify.content-between

     #accordionFaq.accordion.accordion-flush
      .accordion-item
        h3#faq-headingOne.accordion-header
          button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#faq-collapseOne' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='flush-collapseOne')
            | What is Digital Marketing?
        #faq-collapseOne.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby='flush-headingOne' data-bs-parent='#accordionFlushExample')
          .accordion-body
            p Digital marketing involves all marketing efforts that use a digital device or the internet.
      .accordion-item
        h3#faq-headingTwo.accordion-header
          button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#faq-collapseTwo' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='flush-collapseTwo')
            | What Does Digital Marketing Mean For Your Business?
        #faq-collapseTwo.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby='flush-headingTwo' data-bs-parent='#accordionFlushExample')
          .accordion-body
            p With Digital Marketing you can use channels such as social media, email marketing, and blogs to connect and engage with your customers on a local as well global level.
      .accordion-item
        h3#faq-headingThree.accordion-header
          button.accordion-button.collapsed(type='button' data-bs-toggle='collapse' data-bs-target='#faq-collapseThree' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='flush-collapseThree')
            | What Are The Different Types of Digital Marketing?
        #faq-collapseThree.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby='flush-headingThree' data-bs-parent='#accordionFlushExample')
          .accordion-body
           h4.mt-5-mb-2 Content Marketing
           p Content marketing is the process of creating and sharing relevant and consistent content.
           p One of the key goals of content marketing is to provide people with inspirational, life-changing content that adds value to their lives.
           h4 Email Marketing
           p Email marketing is about creating a list of segmented groups of people and crafting an intimate, personalized message for each group. A segmented group might be parents, students, or married couples, and all these groups should be marketed to different groups.
           h4 Search Engine Marketing
           p Search Engine Optimization or SEO is the practice of increasing the traffic to your church website, blogs, newsletters, and social media content.
           h4  Social Media Marketing
           p Social media marketing is the use of social media platforms to connect and engage with your congregation and your local community.
           h4 PPC Marketing
           p Pay-per-click, is a digital marketing model where advertisers run ads on a platform such as Google Ads and pays a fee every time someone clicks on an ad.
           h4 Affiliate Marketing
           p Affiliate marketing involves earning a commission by promoting a product or service made by another company
     p.mt-5 If you would like to see more FAQ's &nbsp;

       a(href="./faq.html" title="faqs") Our Faq page is here



